@startuml deploy
title dropicture - CI/CD pipeline (build, publish and deploy)
footer Author: Amir Redjem   |   2026-06-05   |   v1.0

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam ArrowColor #2F6FED
skinparam ArrowFontColor #41505F
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FDF4F4
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #E6BCBC
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #EEF4FF
skinparam ActorBorderColor #B8CDF3
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #B7E0C9
skinparam CollectionsBackgroundColor #FDF4F4
skinparam CollectionsBorderColor #E6BCBC
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #B8C4D0
skinparam SequenceDividerBackgroundColor #EEF4FF
skinparam SequenceDividerFontColor #41505F
skinparam SequenceGroupBackgroundColor #F6F1FC
skinparam SequenceGroupBorderColor #CDBCE8
skinparam SequenceGroupHeaderFontColor #41505F
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF6EC
skinparam noteBorderColor #F3B27A

actor "Developer" as dev
collections "GitHub Actions\nbuild job (x2)\nmatrix: backend, frontend" as build
database "GHCR\nghcr.io registry" as ghcr
participant "GitHub Actions\ndeploy job\n(env: production)" as deploy
database "S3 backend\ntfstate (eu-west-3)" as s3
participant "Swarm server\nmanager-1 (SSH root)" as srv
participant "Cloudflare\nedge proxy" as cf

== Trigger ==
dev -> build : push main / tag v*.*.* / dispatch\npaths: app/**, compose, nginx.conf,\ngarage.toml, workflow
note right of build
  concurrency: workflow-ref
  cancel-in-progress: false
  fail-fast: false
end note

== Job 1 - Build and publish (per matrix component) ==
build -> build : checkout + setup Buildx
build -> ghcr : docker login\n(GITHUB_TOKEN, packages: write)
build -> build : metadata-action -> tags\nsemver | branch | sha-long | latest (main)
build -> ghcr : build and push linux/amd64\ncache type=gha, scope=component
note over build, ghcr
  amd64 only: the cpx42 target
  is AMD EPYC (x86_64) -
  no QEMU, no arm64 build
end note

== Job 2 - Deploy (needs: build, if: main or tag v*) ==
note over deploy
  concurrency: deploy-production
  env: IMAGE_TAG=sha-<sha>
  + app secrets (POSTGRES_*,
  GARAGE_RPC_SECRET, S3_*)
end note
deploy -> s3 : GET terraform.tfstate\n(AWS creds, read-only)
s3 --> deploy : state JSON
deploy -> deploy : jq outputs.manager_public_ip\nassert non-empty / non-null
deploy -> deploy : ssh-agent (key in memory only,\nnever on disk) + ssh-keyscan
deploy -> srv : docker stack deploy --prune --detach=false\nDOCKER_HOST=ssh://root@MANAGER_IP
srv -> ghcr : pull images :sha-<sha>
note over srv
  rolling updates start-first
  (frontend, backend, pgbouncer)
  stop-first for db, dragonfly, garage
  --detach=false waits for convergence
end note
srv --> deploy : services converged

== Smoke test ==
deploy -> cf : curl -fsSI https://dropicture.com\n(retry 5 x 10s)
cf -> srv : proxied 443\n(Origin CA, Full strict)
srv --> cf : 200
cf --> deploy : 200 OK
deploy --> dev : workflow status

@enduml